<p>Now let's Paint the Tiles.</p>
<p><a href="https://i.ibb.co/PxFBBbH/Screen-Shot-2021-04-08-at-15-59-48.png" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/PxFBBbH/Screen-Shot-2021-04-08-at-15-59-48.png" alt="" class="center" /></a></p>
